        "body": "<p>The issue ended up being fairly simple: the &quot;base path&quot; is set the the path where the command line is being called from.<\/p>\n<p>In my case, we had a statement similar to this...<\/p>\n<p>java -jar /location/of/jar/project.jar<\/p>\n<p>With XSL/CSS in the location of /location/of/jar/xsl<\/p>\n<p>When run, the project was using the location that the command line was called from. Updated references to include the path were successful, or calling it from the jars location instead.<\/p>\n",
        "answer_id": 71181796,
        "question_id": 71159993
    }],
